{"tid":875552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底要幾淫底先會將蛋糕寫成蛋精?","createTime":"2018-10-25T03:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T10:41:58.000Z","uid":59328,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aff0fabb8cfe60e0a96d863930bdaa4c4a9d99bd","tid":875552,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"考評局日前發表TSA報告，小三TSA中文科達標率為86.7%，較往年微升0.4%；英文及數學科達標率分別為80.8%及88%，較往年微跌。報告指出，學生在中文科表現大致平穩，但常犯的「老毛病」仍有待改善，包括錯別字、標點符號等。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，學生常犯的錯別字，一是部件疏漏或缺失，一是錯寫別字。<br />\n<br />\n正寫\t錯別字<br />\n蠟燭\t爉足<br />\n幸福\t辛福<br />\n津津有味\t律律有味<br />\n蛋糕\t蛋精<br />\n依依不捨\t依依不拾<br />\n<br />\n至於標點符號方面，個別學生誤用省略號，例如在「等」後加省略號。部分學生未能適當斷句，又或濫用逗號，個別學生一逗到底，報告建議在日常教學中多加提點學生。<br />\n<br />\n學生英文卷，亦犯串錯字和文法錯誤的情況，例如把「jumped」寫成「jumpped」、「monkey」寫成「moakey」、「favourite」寫成「favourit」等。<br />\n<br />\n數學卷方面，部分學生在長度、距離、重量和容量的量度的題目中，混淆「厘米」(cm)和「毫米」(mm)，把糖果盒長度寫成「91cm」；甚至有學生混淆長度單位和重量單位，把一個橙的重量寫成「重約130cm」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有部分學生亦對「米」和「公里」的概念模糊，例如把香港島與大嶼山之間的距離寫成35「米」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2192304/%E3%80%8C%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E3%80%8D%E5%AF%AB%E6%88%90%E3%80%8C%E8%BE%9B%E7%A6%8F%E3%80%8D%e3%80%80%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%89TSA%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%8F%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%B8%B8%E7%8A%AF%E9%8C%AF%E5%88%A5%E5%AD%97?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2192304%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E6%2588%2590%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25BE%259B%25E7%25A6%258F%25E3%2580%258D%25e3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25B8%2589TSA%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%258A%25AF%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%25AD%2597%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=O5%2FN7kM2dLSIpdI26o7WIDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=cd8a628c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2192304/%E3%80%8C%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E3%80%8D%E5%AF%AB%E6%88%90%E3%80%8C%E8%BE%9B%E7%A6%8F%E3%80%8D%e3%80%80%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%89TSA%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%8F%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%B8%B8%E7%8A%AF%E9%8C%AF%E5%88%A5%E5%AD%97?mtc=10012</a><br />\n<br />\n毛都未出齊就射精 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29d1ebd3e268ad605f6ce38a236edc12cb5adde","tid":875552,"uid":132458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"75f36f3d03e6acbcb4e6f6dad3fe102777a6d1a9","tid":875552,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"將來大學腳控齊齊玩爉足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d58521c0fd208d938c9a46e51bad5059500f67","tid":875552,"uid":158738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a37d88f90ed3ad4087fdaa23a0c878f46e3d78b","tid":875552,"uid":191633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"細個作文要寫一篇遊記<br />\n我將倫敦寫咗做敦倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48080f5a9afd4580bb98c7d1b334d95ca44714ca","tid":875552,"uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a37d88f90ed3ad4087fdaa23a0c878f46e3d78b","tid":875552,"uid":191633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"細個作文要寫一篇遊記<br />\n我將倫敦寫咗做敦倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"一定係特登"},{"pid":"9051a71868182d1c27e36d8c59cb060f316dd0c0","tid":875552,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48080f5a9afd4580bb98c7d1b334d95ca44714ca","tid":875552,"uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a37d88f90ed3ad4087fdaa23a0c878f46e3d78b","tid":875552,"uid":191633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"細個作文要寫一篇遊記<br